# Pinned CI security-audit tooling. Compiled to requirements-audit.lock
# (universal, hash-pinned via uv pip compile) so ci.yml installs the
# audit tool itself with `pip install --require-hashes` — consistent
# with how requirements.lock / requirements-build.lock are installed.
# Avoids an unhashed `pip install pip-audit==X` that would otherwise
# trust whatever PyPI returns for the version pin.
pip-audit==2.10.0
